<plot>"Leave No Soldier" tells the story of two impassioned journeys by two communities of American war veterans who have carried a military oath from the battlefield to the home front. The two groups are divided by their politics, but united in their devotion to dead comrades and their compassionate commitment to "Leave No Fallen Soldier Behind."</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?327972</url></doc>
